#ident	"@(#)bkrs:bkintf.d/backups/Help	1.3.2.2"

ABSTRACT: Backup Service
	The "backup_service" menu allows you to manage the backup side 
	of the backup and restore service.  Functions are provided to 
	determine the backup rotation period, to specify how backups 
	are to be done for file systems and data partitions, to display
	the backup history and backup status logs, to establish lists of
	files that should not be backed up, to respond to operator prompts
	from backup jobs and to schedule backups and the reminder messages
	that backups should be done.

TITLE: Backup Service
